<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: SameOme AlpineKnight</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-22 18:52:13</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>don't know you guys ever had math...  to test the haste effect of ANY item is EASY!!!  if none of you ever figure out the most accurate way of doing it, there it is:<BR>
get a low lvl friend (hopefully you know him in real-life), give him the cloak, and ANY weapon, duel.  Ask him to swin at you for a certain amount of time (maybe 5 mins, hopefully it is not gonna kill ya, LOL), record the number of swins he made.  then un-equip the cloak, swin for another 5 mins, record the number of swins.  for all of you guys that needs an example, here it is:<BR>
<BR>
he swined 96 times in 5 mins w/ the haste item on, 68 times w/o, so <BR>
the % of the haste effect = (96 - 68)/96 * 100 = 29.17%<BR>
<BR>
don't be dumb and try to record the amount of time for each swin LOL...<BR>
now get the idea???? <BR>
<BR>
weapon with haste can be tested in a simular way, figure that out yourself.<BR>
<BR>
i will be testing whichever piece of haste item i get first.<BR>
 <BR>
good luck and hopefully ppl with the items will be posting the correct numbers on the web.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
SameOme AlpineKnight<BR>
28th Pal <BR>
on Vallon Zek<BR>
(a aerospace engineer in real-life =) )</font></td></tr></table>
