<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just camped the Frenzy room for 8 hours.  Only two Frenzied spawned.  The first dropped a ring in hour 1.  Seven hours later the second Frenzied dropped the sash.  In the meantime we pulled the Sentinel and got four pairs of Darkmail gloves.<BR>
<BR>
This camp is actually very good XP all the way up to level 52.<BR>
