<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Duross</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-06 23:06:23</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Only my second day in Lower Guk and I was invited into the frenzy room.  The room was pretty much empty because no one had it camped that time of day.  And within an hour or so we pull the frenzied ghoul.  And low and behold what does he drop?  The FBSS.  Of course I'm thinking "I know I'll never win..."  Prior to this I had won only 2-3 randoms ever for crappy stuff.  Well my time had come and I actually won with a 90 roll.  I couldn't believe it!!! Well I'm very happy with it and will use it till I can get my hands on a haste item with ac like the cof or runed bb.  IMHO its worth camping for.  Best of luck to all who is trying to get it. =)<BR>
<BR>
Duross Keenblade<BR>
40th Paladin<BR>
Prexus Server</font></td></tr></table>
